  "description": "A shipwreck praying. Wreck mode bodyChar 2 with feedback at 0.82 creates allpass-diffused hull resonance — the sound of iron plates vibrating at their natural modes. Filter cutoff at 280 Hz with resonance at 0.7 produces a formant peak that sounds like a voice trapped inside metal. The wreck speaks in low vowels.",
